############################################################
#
#  ILDConfig - package for ilcsoft configuration files
#  such as Marlin steering files, gear geometry files,...
#  related to ILD (or CLIC_ILD)
#
#  01/2012
#  F.Gaede, DESY
############################################################

This new package just combines the old packages StandardConfig and MokkaDBConfig,
which will be obsolete form now on (iLCSoft release v01-13-03).


The configuration files in this release should work with the following Mokka models:
  ILD_O1_v03
  ILD_O2_v03
  ILD_O3_v03



subdirectories:

 StandardConfig/
 ----------------
    current
    -------
    current example files for running Mokka and Marlin
    (see: ./current/README for mini howto on using (this version of) ilcsoft )
     
    
    mc2008
    ------
    configuration files for 2008 Monte Carlo production for LOI
    
    
    clic_cdr
    ------
    configuration files for CLIC CDR production (2011)


 MokkaDBConfig/
 -------------

    current dump of the Mokka DB: mokka-dbdump.sql.tgz

    
    scripts
    -------
    scripts for related to running Mokka or the Mokka DB 




 versions:
 ========

 -----------
| v01-13-06 |
 -----------
    - updated mokka dump: mokka-07-07-p08-dbdump.sql.tgz (2012-05-16 - 18:33:52)
    - updated Clupatra steering parameters to v00-06
    - changed steering parameters for the Cellular Automaton in ForwardTracking
    - updated TruthTracker parameters
    - Added TrackSubsetProcessor to the standard steer. It combines the tracks of SiliconTracking_MarlinTrk and ForwardTracking to one collection of tracks. This collections is then passed to FullLDCTracking_MarlinTrk
    - added MokkaDBConfig init.sh script
    - added scripts to run sim/rec jobs on the grid
    - moved particle.tbl from MokkaDBConfig to StandardConfig/current
    - fixed cleanup of mysql socket in mokka-wrapper.sh

 -----------
| v01-13-05 |
 -----------
   - switched to versioning scheme that is parallel to iLCSoft 
     (additional releases should be patch releases v01-13-05-p0x) 
   
   - reactivated ForwardTracking and changed steering parameter BestSubsetFinder to SubsetHopfieldNN
   - added new mokka dump: mokka-07-07-p07-dbdump.sql.tgz (2012-03-29 - 17:56:36)
   - updated Clupatra steering section
   - updated planar digitiser and RecoMCTruthLinker for silicon strip hits
   - activated lcioDetailedTRKHitMode for all tracking detectors

